HEADWORD: Substantialness
<hw>Sub*stan"tial*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of
being substantial; <as>as, the <ex>substantialness</ex> of a wall or
column</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

